{"parentUuid":"789c5e39-d4e8-4f55-81e9-dbcf83502266","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"795b6292-899f-43d1-822d-8e0cc35d6b7d","agentId":"a4053cef465153bd0","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01KVYP6M6rVb4anfVW1CAak1","type":"tool_result","content":"On branch feature/usage-export\nChanges not staged for commit:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to update what will be committed)\n  (use \"git restore <file>...\" to discard changes in working directory)\n\tmodified:   .github/workflows/pipeline-ci.yml\n\tmodified:   PROJECT.md\n\tmodified:   docs/system_architecture.md\n\tmodified:   src/api/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/main.py\n\tmodified:   src/repositories/README.md\n\tmodified:   src/repositories/usage_repo.py\n\tmodified:   src/services/README.md\n\tmodified:   tests/README.md\n\tmodified:   tests/integration/README.md\n\nUntracked files:\n  (use \"git add <file>...\" to include in what will be committed)\n\tdocs/decisions/feature/usage-export/\n\tsrc/api/csv_export.py\n\tsrc/api/routes/usage_export.py\n\tsrc/api/schemas/usage_export.py\n\tsrc/services/usage_export_service.py\n\ttests/integration/test_usage_export_endpoint.py\n\ttests/integration/test_usage_export_perf.py\n\ttests/test_csv_export.py\n\ttests/test_schemas_usage_export.py\n\ttests/test_usage_export_service.py\n\nno changes added to commit (use \"git add\" and/or \"git commit -a\")\n=====DIFF STAT=====\n .github/workflows/pipeline-ci.yml |   9 +--\n PROJECT.md                        |   8 +--\n docs/system_architecture.md       |  96 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++-\n src/api/README.md                 |  13 ++--\n src/main.py                       |   2 +\n src/repositories/README.md        |  14 ++--\n src/repositories/usage_repo.py    | 136 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-\n src/services/README.md            |  10 +--\n tests/README.md                   |   5 +-\n tests/integration/README.md       |   2 +\n 10 files changed, 266 insertions(+), 29 deletions(-)","is_erro